description._content: Collection: NASA Image eXchange Collection Title: Scout Project Description: Spectators--mainly the families of NASA employees--usually filled the makeshift grandstand at Wallops Island to witness the launch of NASA's small unmanned rockets." This gathering was to watch the launch of S-113 on June 28, 1963.
